						></path>
					</svg>
					Contribute a Link
				</a>
			</div>

			<!-- Bots Section -->
			<div
				class="bg-selfcare-blue/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-selfcare-blue/20"
			>
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-selfcare-600 mb-4">selfcare.tech bots</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm">
					I made a few Mastodon bots if you'd like to follow them. There are reminders for selfcare
					practice and the occasional link as well.
				</p>
